        "custom_liquid": "<div style=\"padding: 80px 40px; background: #f7f7f7; text-align: center;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 28px; font-size: 64px; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">\n      What You Can Expect from Growealth\n    </h2>\n    <p style=\"max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 80px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.8; color: #555;\">\n      Growealth focuses on helping home growers and small indoor cultivation setups find practical, reliable products with less confusion and a better buying experience.\n    </p>\n\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; align-items: start;\">\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"width: 150px; height: 150px; margin: 0 auto 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4EB99F; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 54px;\">✓</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; line-height: 1.2;\">Selected Products</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top: 24px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;\">Carefully Curated Choices</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"width: 150px; height: 150px; margin: 0 auto 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4EB99F; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 54px;\">i</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; line-height: 1.2;\">Clear Information</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top: 24px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;\">Easy-to-Understand Product Details</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"width: 150px; height: 150px; margin: 0 auto 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4EB99F; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 54px;\">↗</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; line-height